# ============================================================
# ENTITY DETAIL POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: detail
subdomain: entity-detail
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Defines policy rules for entity detail.

policy_focus:
- public summary versus internal detail separation
- sealed profile handling
- archival retention of historical snapshots
- revision authority over entity profile detail

disclosure_matrix:
- public_summary: public allowed
- internal_profile: public denied
- sealed_profile: high-trust only
- historical_snapshot: audit or authorized history mode only

validation_rules:
- entity detail must declare disclosure class.
- sealed profile detail must not be published publicly.
- historical snapshots must preserve snapshot labeling.
